SUMMARY:Nature Journaling 101 – CANCELLED
DESCRIPTION:Learn the basics of nature journaling – documenting your nature observations in a notebook – in this hands on class for adults! You’ll receive a kit with all the tools you’ll need to get started and walk away with multiple finished pages. No art skills required and we welcome beginners through seasoned nature journalers! \nCost: $22. $20 Museum members\nRegister
URL:https://naturalsciences.org/calendar/event/nature-journaling-101-4-2026/
